collections.name: The Jack of Blades
collections.description:
This collection owns 3000 unique collectible characters, each with verifiable ownership recorded on the Ethereum block chain, inspired the creation of the ERC-721 standard.

The “Jack of Blades” refers to the individual that allows blind ambition, the homicidal lust for power to take complete control of his/her heart and turn it to stone. Whether serial-killer, revolutionary, cut-throat industrialist or terrorist, this is a person whose sense of grandeur and need to “lord” it over others is so self-consuming that they have no qualms about destroying society to achieve their aims, and most often, that is precisely what they end up doing. They become the unwitting agents of their own destruction.

Minters of our NFT can claim an exclusive silver jewelry piece from Tartaria Jewelry engraved with One-of-a-Kind NFT's token number—a wearable masterpiece that unites the digital and physical worlds.

collections.name: Spring Bot
collections.description: Dive into the enchanting world of Spring Bot, an imaginative NFT collection where whimsy meets innovation. Each piece in the collection showcases a playful robotic character brought to life with vibrant colors and surreal charm, merging the futuristic with the fantastical.

collections.name: Lone Echoes
collections.description:
Lone Echoes is a gallery of ethereal one-of-one creations — each piece a fragment of a forgotten dream or an uncomfortable truth, suspended in cosmic stillness.

Animals, spirits, and strange personalities drift through surreal nightscapes, some whispering forgotten memories, others shouting the absurdity of modern life.
From soft moments of vulnerability to sharp stabs of satire, every piece is a solitary echo — emotional, ironic, or otherworldly.

No roadmap. No series. Just echoes.
Some cry. Some laugh. A few demand everything.
Every work exists alone, yet resonates together — like distant stars in a sky only some can see.

Each piece is rare. Each holds its own presence. And once it’s gone, it will never return.

collections.name: The Mori Hound
collections.description:
This collection owns 3000 unique collectible characters, each with verifiable ownership recorded on the Ethereum block chain, inspired the creation of the ERC-7

The Mori Hound is part of the Kali Yuga collection, created by Tartaria Jewelry. Mori translates to Death in Latin. Thus, the Death Hound represents the mythical dogs of destruction throughout history. There is Fenrir, the giant wolf of Norse mythology which brought on Ragnarök, the final death of all the gods. There is also the great Black Hound of medieval Europe reportedly seen right before tragedy or death, a forever omen of destruction. In this design the dog skull is biting through the Ouroboros snake, representing the endless cycle of time and creation, and so severs time itself, bringing on the final ending of all things.

Minters of our NFT can claim an exclusive silver jewelry piece from Tartaria Jewelry engraved with One-of-a-Kind NFT's token number—a wearable masterpiece that unites the digital and physical worlds.

collections.description: “Issue Zero” is the prequel nobody saw coming. A riot of neon, grit, and glitch, this debut drop from internet-native artist SkullTantan reads like a pulp origin story from an alternate timeline. Cyber-ronin, masked punks, and antiheroes-in-the-making flash across 50 one-of-one works, each a frozen frame from a comic that doesn’t exist (yet). Submitted through Discord and designed and brought to life through Orangehare’s in-house production process, “Issue Zero” is a collection of cover stories waiting to become canon.

collections.name: The Cosmic Wanderer
collections.description:
Cosmic Wanderer: A Journey Through the Cosmos

Embark on an interstellar odyssey with Cosmic Wanderer, a limited collection of 50 unique NFTs that capture the awe-inspiring beauty of the universe! Each piece features a lone astronaut drifting through vibrant, surreal galaxies—think swirling Orion Nebulas, towering Pillars of Creation, and fiery Supernova Explosions. With shimmering nebula suits, animated twinkling stars, and swirling cosmic dust, these artworks come alive with a "living" feel.

Why You’ll Love It:

Dynamic Art: Watch the galaxy shift colors over time, creating a mesmerizing experience.

Cosmic Wanderer is more than art—it’s a piece of the universe you can own. Perfect for space enthusiasts, sci-fi lovers, and NFT collectors who crave exploration, solitude, and the beauty of the unknown. Don’t miss your chance to claim a spot in this cosmic journey! 🚀✨
